{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- even if I didn't know them, I think they need us, and-- and we-- whatever we could, we share.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We bought the first bonds-- what we had, whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We helped-- medication, anything-- medicine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they remember, some of that-- them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would come to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There, everybody comes, no matter from where.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I found people what they-- accidentally, I visit my husband's friends, which from their hometown.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Somebody came to visit them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said, you look so familiar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she heard the name, Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I told her my maiden name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She asked me, so I told her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So her father was my daddy's best friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's funny how close-- how funny how things are-- circumstance can bring together people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we constantly correspond with each other-- and very devoted-- and a lot of people which we are close with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell me about the life that you and Moris built here, about the work that you did, and about raising your daughter, and-- and any grandchildren that you have.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only one-- first of all, I have only one daughter, which her name is Rita.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My married name is Frumin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she finished college.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I work-- first of all, I did apply to associate, although-- but difficult to speak English.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was desperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I need something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I applied to Kelly Company, that they take off the-- from the wages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got the job going through the intelligent test, which I passed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think he-- the manager thought I'm German, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, what happen, I applied to the office, and I was working for the associate investment company before we opened our store, our own business.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And until-- they-- they didn't know I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
